 deutetrabenazine should be monitored more closely whenever a strong CYP450 2D6 inhibitor (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/28248/', '', 'Dexfenfluramine, Naltrexone, Ephedrine, Phentermine, Orlistat, Lorcaserin, Diethylpropion, Mazindol, Levomilnacipran, Oxitriptan, Vortioxetine, More', 'Inotersen, Riluzole, Tafamidis', 1767369485);
